76561198088380930,Recommended,225000,16633091,"Posted: 22 June, 2015",all,emasterslake,"Chronicles was the last game to use polygonic graphics for character designs and levels as well as a follow up to Last Revelation. The fate of Lara in the last game was unclear, as in this game her friends believe that she is dead and end up recounting stories of her previous adventures. All of the game play focuses on a series of four different flashbacks, while the present day events are only shown in the FMVs. The game show cases slightly more improvements on the gameplay while the graphics are about the same. Levels are hard at times, but anyone who's played these games will know what to expect. I am a fan of origin stories so I do enjoy the concept of a game that delves into other adventures Lara had besides the adventures we already seen her in the previous games."
